{
  "stem": "5430.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the townspeople, the Jewish people who we befriended and were very happy that we worked together, cried.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were citizens because they had no choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They lived there so they-- once they overran that part of the country, they became citizens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were [RUSSIAN], or refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we stuck to our version of being Polish, and we're going to go home as soon as the war is over.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We thought the war  would be over in a couple of months or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So anyway, they remained in town, and we were shipped out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As we found out later, it was Siberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Took us over two weeks to travel in the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, once a day, they would bring in a cauldron of soup, kasha.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that's a-- I don't know what the-- and-- and I think some bread, also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the train would not open up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Way, way into the-- further, and deep into the country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- once we were, I think, past the Ural mountains, which is Northern Russia, they started opening up the-- the trains, because we had no way of running anyway.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody told us where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember they would-- that-- that-- that toilet that they created for it got so-- so bad that my father and the other families who were on the train decided-- we threw it out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- but at that point, they allowed us, to you know, every time they made a stop, we would all run to the sides of the train, to the woods or whatever there was, to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, there was our family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- I think there were four families in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
